  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 68551,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それらに対し、長槍を主武器とした兵三千が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Against them, three thousand soldiers armed mainly with long spears,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68552,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "散々に突きかかる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "fiercely thrust forward."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68553,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「三人一組で一匹殺せ！　奴らぁ混乱してやがる！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kill one beast with a team of three! They're in confusion!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68554,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「んー、ちょっと多かったなぁ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, that was a little too many..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68555,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　千くらいだと良かったんだけど」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It would've been better if there were about a thousand.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68556,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "『魔軍本隊、動き出しました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "'The demon army main force has started moving."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68557,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　来ちゃったりしますよー』",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They're coming!'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68558,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい了解」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Understood.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68559,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "篠田の手には、司令部に繋がる魔法電話がある。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In Shinoda's hand was a magical phone connected to the command headquarters."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68560,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "センサー地蔵のひとつを抱えさせた器兵コプターを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A mechanical soldier copter carrying one of the sensor Jizo statues"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68561,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ポピンズ技師が操り、空から撮った映像を元に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was operated by Poppins engineers, using footage taken from the sky"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68562,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ヌヌハラたち司令部の通信兵がナビゲートを行う。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and the command communication soldiers like Nunuhara guided the operation."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68563,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "こうする事で、篠田は敵軍の動きに関する情報を、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "By doing this, Shinoda was able to"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68564,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "かなり正確な範囲で押さえていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "keep track of the enemy troop movements with quite accurate details."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68565,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「火縄銃、二射目お願いします。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Matchlocks, second shots please."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68566,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　確認後、撮影機以外の器兵で、アレ撒いちゃって」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After confirmation, with mechanical soldiers other than the camera ones, spread that stuff.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68567,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ははっ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha ha!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68568,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーぅ……やっぱり、それでもこんなものか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Phew... After all, it's just about this much."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68569,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　んん……仕方ないよね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hmm... It can't be helped, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68570,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「逃げ場はない！　叩き殺せ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No escape! Crush them to death!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68571,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "雪崩をうって、魔軍本隊が殺到した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Like an avalanche, the demon army main force surged forward."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68572,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "山道いっぱいに広がった魔軍は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The demon army spread wide across the mountain path,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68573,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ただぶつかって押し潰すだけでも",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and even just by colliding and crushing,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68574,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "殲滅するには充分すぎる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it was more than enough to annihilate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68575,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぐっ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68576,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "と、その時、十数万の魔軍の鬨の声に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then, amid the war cries of hundreds of thousands of demons,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68577,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "掻き消されそうになりながら、銃声が響いた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "a gunshot rang out, nearly drowned out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68578,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ッ、二射目…………合図、来たぞ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The second shot... the signal has come!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68579,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　帰り木使用許可ッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Permission to use the Return Wood granted!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68580,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なぁっ！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"W-What!?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68581,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "人間達の懐が、手元が、不意に光ったかと思うと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Suddenly, the bosoms and hands of the humans shone,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68582,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その姿は忽然と消え失せた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and their figures vanished without a trace."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68583,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "たどり着いた頃には、影も形もない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "By the time the enemy caught up, there was no sign or shadow of them."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68584,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「に、逃げられた、だと……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"T-They escaped...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68585,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれだけの数を拾いあげるほどの帰り木を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To have prepared that much Return Wood to pick up so many of them..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68586,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　用意していたとは……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "such preparation...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68587,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "進撃を停止し、しばし呆然とした魔軍の頭上で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As the advancing demon army halted in stunned silence, above their heads,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68588,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何かの音がした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there was a sound."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68589,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"... ?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68590,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……！　しょ、将軍、伏せッ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...! G-General, get down...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68591,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お、あ……………ッ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"O-Ah...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68592,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "十数機の器兵コプタ―に満載したプチハニー爆弾が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Petit Hanny bombs loaded onto a dozen mechanical soldier copters"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68593,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ひとつ残らず魔軍の頭上に降り注いでいた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "rained down without a single one missing over the demon army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68594,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "強烈な爆発が魔軍を襲った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A powerful explosion struck the demon army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68595,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "個々が強靱な魔物兵のこと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Since each was a strong demon soldier,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68596,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "爆発を耐えきった者も少なからず存在したが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there were quite a few who withstood the blast,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68597,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "広範囲に注いだ爆撃は魔軍の動きを堰き止めた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but the wide-ranging bombardment blocked the demon army's advance."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68598,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぐっ、ぐおおおお……ッ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh, guoooh...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68599,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……！　ま、まずい！　崖崩れが来る！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...! T-This is bad! A landslide is coming!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68600,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　たッ、退避……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "R-Retreat...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68601,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「に、逃げ場、ありません！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"T-There’s no place to run!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68602,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "爆撃のいくらかが岩山に注がれ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Some of the bombs fell onto the rocky mountain,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68603,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それが魔軍への追撃となった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "which turned into a pursuit against the demon army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68604,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "派手な崖崩れに少なくない魔物兵が巻き込まれ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The flashy landslide swept up a considerable number of demon soldiers,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68605,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そのうちの何割かは土砂の中に埋もれた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "some of whom got buried under the debris."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68606,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お、おぉ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"O-Oh...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68607,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「空が使えてお金があるならこうしちゃうよねぇ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you can use the sky and have money, you'd do something like this, right?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68608,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひどいなぁ、プチハニー爆弾」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "How awful, Petit Hanny bombs."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68609,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いえ、そうですが……しかし、篠田殿もお見事……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, that's true... but Shinoda-dono is also impressive..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68610,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　このように、一方的な……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "to achieve such a one-sided...\""
    }
  ]
}

